      "front": "い-adjective (present affirmative)",
      "back": "〜いです",
      "romanized": "~i desu",
      "grammarNote": "い-adjectives end in い and conjugate by changing that い. Present affirmative: keep い + desu. おもしろい → おもしろいです."
